indicator-virtual-box (1.0.41-1) precise; urgency=low

  * Bug fix: When autostarting a VM (or VMs), the time delay of 5 seconds
    after the VM is started and before updating the menu was insufficient when
    the host was cold booting.  The delay has been increased to 1 minute to
    give ample time for the host to start up and VBoxManage to correctly
    identify running VMs.

